He's alive.

567
00:51:05,560 --> 00:51:06,891
So shoot him.

568
00:51:19,840 --> 00:51:21,842
I have to go.
I have to go.

569
00:51:22,920 --> 00:51:25,241
I'm sorry, Mr. Glass.
I'm sorry.

570
00:51:26,160 --> 00:51:28,000
I'm sorry, I'm sorry.

