You woke me up.
Mmm-hmm.

602
00:57:37,640 --> 00:57:39,881
You said you saw
twenty Ree by the creek.

603
00:57:39,960 --> 00:57:41,962
Well, yeah,
twenty, a dozen...

604
00:57:42,040 --> 00:57:43,121
