626
00:58:42,920 --> 00:58:44,285
The Ree.

627
00:58:44,360 --> 00:58:45,691
What of them?

628
00:58:46,520 --> 00:58:48,443
Tell me, did you see 'em?

629
00:58:48,520 --> 00:58:50,682
Put your rifle down.
Did you see the Ree?

630
00:58:52,880 --> 00:58:54,120
No.

631
00:58:55,360 --> 00:58:57,203
Not a single one.

632
00:58:59,800 --> 00:59:03,361
