01:44:21,680 --> 01:44:23,444
Shh...

766
01:44:24,880 --> 01:44:26,803
Don't make a sound.

767
01:44:41,080 --> 01:44:44,482
I will get a horse.

768
01:44:48,760 --> 01:44:52,162
I'll cut off your balls.

769
01:45:07,720 --> 01:45:10,530
Where is Toussaint?

770
01:45:12,920 --> 01:45:15,287
Come here...

771
01:46:06,520 --> 01:46:08,443
- May I join you?
