772
01:46:08,680 --> 01:46:09,681
Yeah?

773
01:46:09,800 --> 01:46:10,801
Yes.

774
01:46:10,880 --> 01:46:14,726
I was wondering when we might
be getting paid for that haul.

775
01:46:14,800 --> 01:46:17,485
'Cause them pelts
we collected

776
01:46:17,600 --> 01:46:19,284
