you know...

777
01:46:19,360 --> 01:46:20,964
...under a couple foot
of dirt and snow.

778
01:46:21,040 --> 01:46:23,691
But that ain't
my fault.

779
01:46:23,760 --> 01:46:25,330
I'm waiting for
Captain Leavenworth

780
01:46:25,440 --> 01:46:27,124
to arrive
with his army.

781
01:46:27,200 --> 01:46:29,487
Then we'll have
enough men...

782
01:46:29,560 --> 01:46:32,291
