nobody gets paid.

788
01:46:45,720 --> 01:46:47,722
Listen here, all right?

789
01:46:48,080 --> 01:46:51,721
I was hired to trap 'em.
I wasn't hired to guard 'em.

790
01:46:52,080 --> 01:46:56,449
